Psalm 62-4 <t>They only plan to thrust him down from his <f>ⓗ</f>high position. </t><t>They take pleasure in falsehood. </t><t><f>ⓘ</f>They bless with their mouths, </t><t>but inwardly they curse. <pb/><i>Selah</i> <pb/></t>
